igin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><b>Бенефициары паллиативного ухода:</b></span></p>Пациенты всех возрастов с хроническими прогрессирующими заболеваниями с ограниченным прогнозом для жизни до 12 месяцев, с не контролируемыми симптомами, психоэмоциональными страданиями и представляющими определенный уровень зависимости.</p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br>В зависимости от тяжести состояния, бенефициары медицинского ухода на дому подразделяются:</p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><b>Полностью зависимый</b></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\">&nbsp;- пациент, который не может выполнять три или более ежедневные функции, без помощи другого человека и нуждается в медицинском уходе.</span></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><br></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><b>Частично зависимый</b></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\">&nbsp;- пациент, который не может выполнять как минимум две основные ежедневные функции, без помощи другого человека и по причине тяжелого состояния здоровья нуждается в медицинском уходе на дому.</span></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><br></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><b>Зависимый</b></span><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><b>&nbsp;</b>– пациент, который выполняет основные ежедневные функции без посторонней помощи, но по причине хронических заболеваний нуждается в услугах медицинского ухода на дому.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section>', '2019-06-12 20:00:39', '2019-06-12 20:00:39'),
(29, 3, 5, '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">Asociația Obștească „MEDLIFE„ activează din 2009. Înregistrată la Ministerul Justiției al Republicii Moldova la data de 05.06.2009, ca organizație non-guvernamentală non-profit.&nbsp;<br></span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">În 2009 Camera Înregistrării de Stat a obținut o Licență pentru asistență medicală ambulatorie și asistență medicală la domiciliu .<br></span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">Din anul 2010 și pînă în prezent AO ”MEDLIFE” este acreditată de Ministerul Sănătății al Republicii Moldova.<br></span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">Din anul 2009 și pînă în prezent AO ”MEDLIFE” este licențiată în:</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\">Acordarea asistenței medicale consultative – curative, în domeniul medicinii interne, chirurgie și ginecologie de ambulatoriu, îngrijiri paliative și medico-sociale la domiciliu</span>.</b></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</span>AO ”MEDLIFE” este contractată cu Compania Națională de Asigurări în Medicină din 2010. &nbsp;Contractul prevede acordarea asistenţei medicale în cadrul asigurărilor obligatorii de asistenţă medicală – ingrijiri medicale la domiciliu. Din anul 2013, concomitent, prestează și servicii de îngrijiri paliative la domiciliu. Sursa finanțării de bază este FAOAM (Fondurile Asigurării Obligatorii de Asistență Medicală).</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/images/istoria-1.jpg\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; width: 50%;\"><img src=\"/images/istoria-2.jpg\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; width: 50%;\"></div><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><b>Scopul nostru</b></p></span><p style=\"text-align: center; \">Îmbunătățirea calității vieții pacienților incurabili și a rudelor acestora, sprijinirea stării lor psihoemoțională, înconjurarea pacientului cu atenție și acordarea de asistență medicală simptomatică la nivel înalt.</p><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><b style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">Activitatea de bază</b></p></span><p style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Îngrijiri medicale comunitare la domiciliu<br>Îngrijiri paliative la domiciliu<br>Asistență medicală de ambulatoriu</p><p></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</span></div><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><p style=\"\"></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"><b>Principalele direcții de dezvoltare&nbsp;</b></span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">:</span></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Creșterea volumului prestării serviciilor de îngrijiri medicale la domiciliu;<br>Extinderea zonelor de acoperire de prestare a serviciilor de îngrijiri medicale la domiciliu pe teritoriul Republicii Moldova;<br>&nbsp;Acordarea serviciilor de calitate înaltă</p><p></p></span><p></p>', '2019-06-12 20:06:29', '2019-06-12 20:06:29');
